item.title: Game Pacman Maze 3D
item.description: Gamers are offered a very unusual performance of the popular game. The view in it is from the first person, and the action takes place in a three-dimensional maze. As before, you need to collect vitamins and avoid encounters with monsters in the maze. To help the player is given a map located in the upper left corner of the screen. It depicts the labyrinth itself, all the characters and tablets.
